  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a pilot study to determine the usefulness of new brachytherapy device that utilizes
      active components (palladium-103) of standard devices in a novel configuration, which may
      benefit basal cell and squamous cell carcinoma patients by providing conformal radiation
      therapy to the surface of the skin.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
